data.description: Happy New Year! Why not treat yourself to this HUGE 3 level Clearing Home for the start of 2024?  You won't find many like this in the area.  The house is complete with 5 bedrooms, updated gas fireplace, full basement and many upgrades.  In the summertime enjoy time out on the expansive back deck and relax in the swimming pool complete with a brand new lining (2023).  Store your cars and tools in the 2.5 car garage and get away from life's stresses in the finished basement.  Enjoy cooking and entertaining in the remodeled kitchen (2020) that boasts new appliances, new cabinets, marble countertop, soft close drawers, and new lighting.  There are too many upgrades to list; including a new AC unit (2023), new washer and dryer (2021), new roof (2018) and many smart home features.   All you have to do is move in and enjoy.
